org.apache.http
Class HttpHeaders

java.lang.Object
  org.apache.http.HttpHeaders

public final class HttpHeaders
extends Object

Constants enumerating the HTTP headers. All headers defined in RFC1945 (HTTP/1.0), RFC2616 (HTTP/1.1), and RFC2518 (WebDAV) are listed.

Since:
4.1
